images of women scientists at work the clayman institute for gender research skip to main content standford university the clayman institute for gender research the clayman institute for gender research home programs news strategic focus events about research fellowships library media center you are here home other media resources images of women scientists at work images of women scientists at work the institute has recently initiated a women scientists at work photography series sponsored by the marilyn yalom fund the women scientists at work series features students based in professor adina paytan's laboratory in the earth sciences department photographed by bay area photographer nicolo sertorio the image series shows real women scientists working in a real laboratory situation the institute is very grateful to professor paytan for making her laboratory available for this project visit nicolo sertorio's website to see examples of his previous work www photonicolo com donate make a donation social links facebook twitter youtube scribd contact serra house 589 capistrano way stanford ca 94305 8640 map 650 723 1994 gender email stanford edu
